### Setup perfil de seller (BOOKSTORE) - precisa de token de user BOOKSTORE
POST http://localhost:8080/sellers/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bookstore_token}}

{
  "publicName": "Sebo da Esquina",
  "description": "Sebo especializado em livros academicos e classicos da literatura brasileira.",
  "city": "Sao Paulo",
  "state": "SP",
  "neighborhood": "Vila Madalena"
}

### Ver perfil de seller do user logado
GET http://localhost:8080/sellers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{bookstore_token}}

### Criar listing via ISBN (INDIVIDUAL_SELLER - auto-provision de seller)
POST http://localhost:8080/listings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{individual_token}}

{
  "isbn": "9788535911725",
  "priceCents": 4500,
  "condition": "BOM",
  "conditionNotes": "Capa com leve desgaste nas bordas",
  "description": "Edicao classica da Companhia das Letras, excelente para estudo.",
  "photos": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/foto-capa.jpg",
      "position": 0,
      "photoType": "COVER_FRONT"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/foto-lombada.jpg",
      "position": 1,
      "photoType": "SPINE_BACK"
    }
  ]
}

### Criar listing manual (sem ISBN)
POST http://localhost:8080/listings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bookstore_token}}

{
  "manualBookData": {
    "title": "Introducao a Analise Real",
    "authors": "Elon Lages Lima",
    "publisher": "IMPA",
    "publicationYear": 2000,
    "language": "pt-BR",
    "academicAreas": ["Matematica", "Analise"]
  },
  "priceCents": 8000,
  "condition": "COMO_NOVO",
  "description": "Livro em otimo estado, sem anotacoes.",
  "photos": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/analise-real-capa.jpg",
      "position": 0,
      "photoType": "COVER_FRONT"
    }
  ]
}

### Listar meus anuncios
GET http://localhost:8080/listings/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{individual_token}}

### BUYER tentando criar listing (esperado: 403)
POST http://localhost:8080/listings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{buyer_token}}

{
  "isbn": "9788535911725",
  "priceCents": 3000,
  "condition": "BOM",
  "photos": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/foto.jpg",
      "position": 0,
      "photoType": "COVER_FRONT"
    }
  ]
}

### Busca fuzzy de books
GET http://localhost:8080/books/search/fuzzy?title=Memorias%20Postumas

### Listing com 0 fotos (esperado: 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/listings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{individual_token}}

{
  "isbn": "9788535911725",
  "priceCents": 3000,
  "condition": "BOM",
  "photos": []
}

### Listing com preco < 100 (esperado: 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/listings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{individual_token}}

{
  "isbn": "9788535911725",
  "priceCents": 50,
  "condition": "BOM",
  "photos": [
    {
      "url": "https://example.com/foto.jpg",
      "position": 0,
      "photoType": "COVER_FRONT"
    }
  ]
}

